Guy Hands’s Terra Firma Sets Deadline for Odeon Bids, Times Says

-- B y   G a v i n   F i n c h
-- 
2011-05-29T09:00:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/guy-hands-s-terra-firma-sets-deadline-for-odeon-bids-times-says.html
Guy Hands ’s Terra Firma Capital
Partners Ltd. has set a June 3 deadline for bids for the U.K.
cinema chain Odeon, the Sunday Times reported, without saying
where it obtained the information.  Private-equity firm BC Partners Ltd. is preparing an offer
with the Ontario Municipal Employees Retirement System, a
Canadian pension fund, the newspaper said. Hands hopes to sell
Odeon for more than 1.2 billion pounds ($2 billion), the Times
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gavin Finch in London at 
 gfinch@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Evans at 
 eevans3@bloomberg.net  